Kim Buk soon Big Nambi House?️ 623 m from ?Klairs Seoul?If you want to have a good Korean meal experience, there is no place like ?Kim Buk Soon?s Big Pot House??The large pot where they boil jjigae is called ?Nambi??This restaurant sells one of the most representative Korean foods, kimchi jjigae. Kimchi jjigae is a dish with kimchi, broth, and other ingredients that are boiled together.You choose the ingredients you want such as tuna or pork, and a hot kimchi jjigae is prepared for you in a pot.The flavor is very strong and deep.It can be a little spicy, so the rolled omelette is a must-have.I emptied a bowl of rice in an instant.It was a nice, filling meal.?️ 15 Apgujeong-ro 2-gil, Gangnam-gu,seoul, Korea?️ Open Hour: 10:20 - 22:00 ?️ Open: Monday to Saturday (Closed in Sunday)..#seoulmate #?울메이??KlairsSeoul #?레?스?울#김북순?남비집
